{"tid":1955901,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【功夫再好】外籍確診患者拒抽血發惡　女護士遭毆打咬傷臉落淚","createTime":"2020-04-02T20:26:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T00:10:55.000Z","uid":224066,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a728130854678bb02040920e4489c8839c7a0a","tid":1955901,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T20:26:42.000Z","msg":"COVID-19新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情持續，<span style=\"color: red;\">廣州市第八人民醫院一名47歲的尼日利亞籍確診男病人OKONKWONWOYE CHIKA PATRICK，周三（4月1日）上午約7時被一名汪姓女護士要求抽血檢查，但他未有配合，反而毆打咬傷女護士</span>；警方其後將惡漢拘捕，並進行刑事調查。<br />\n<br />\n當日該名男患者被汪女要抽血檢查時拒絕配合，更嘗試強行走出隔離病房，汪女見狀立即上前攔截，卻被推倒地上毆打，臉部更被咬傷。網上影片顯示，汪女滿臉傷痕，頸背滿是紅印及瘀青，當被問及傷勢，汪女忍不住落淚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4254672/org/c029a418914f853aa195f3382af9d8b8.jpg/GWpV2MbxlFAkkqyfC9e_qfjg9LStxMxtvkGbYr5Bm2I?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4254672%2Forg%2Fc029a418914f853aa195f3382af9d8b8.jpg%2FGWpV2MbxlFAkkqyfC9e_qfjg9LStxMxtvkGbYr5Bm2I%3Fv%3Dw640&h=de9f7ee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經法醫檢查，汪女臉、頸及腰部均有損傷，鑑定為輕微傷。院方表示，男事主上月20日入境，接受病毒核酸檢測後確診，同月23日被送院隔離治療，目前其核酸檢測顯示他的體內仍帶有病毒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4254673/org/9d000a605ac7b7c4c48e1fa90c9db836.jpg/lATlkMqMRlBceLi-Gahkl2IaiaxmLIsw140pjteNKY4?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4254673%2Forg%2F9d000a605ac7b7c4c48e1fa90c9db836.jpg%2FlATlkMqMRlBceLi-Gahkl2IaiaxmLIsw140pjteNKY4%3Fv%3Dw640&h=10d2000a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n院方表示，現已加強內部隔離區的保安措施；警方則已立刑事案進行調查，而行兇患者將在監管下隔離治療，待康復後將採取刑事強制措施，並依法嚴懲。<br />\n<br />\n事件引起網民關注，紛留言稱<span style=\"color: red;\">「這件事必須嚴懲，必須要讓這些自以為是的東西付出代價」、「在中國撒野絕對有後果的」</span>、「醫護人員都是我們的寶貝，尤其是身在一線的，不要讓他們受委屈」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=79uqu9WuPeE&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D79uqu9WuPeE%26feature%3Demb_logo&h=230d6f4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d3c48bdca4ab18059e8410c9d929fd4a1ba448f","tid":1955901,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T20:29:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a10a75b00d2b1f4a0513b4403732099c6c62333","tid":1955901,"uid":189109,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T20:33:53.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb5b1d4e4525db1b1f7efd7d5211e4d8a10ea72","tid":1955901,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T20:38:33.000Z","msg":"奶jer人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5941cee0534e76ed93e3ab6dbaa68d29268e750d","tid":1955901,"uid":327354,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T20:40:39.000Z","msg":"一睇相就覺得over了"},{"pid":"39249040c2a78d6ef47e26ef039c6eab7ff4dc6e","tid":1955901,"uid":14816,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T20:55:17.000Z","msg":"髮線好高"},{"pid":"acdc6276e18d7b837979212155dcfd7629b0931e","tid":1955901,"uid":123053,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T21:26:27.000Z","msg":"女人係低打"},{"pid":"7065be3d9fa91067c36fabac0f2dc17ca72eeee0","tid":1955901,"uid":342282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9bb5b1d4e4525db1b1f7efd7d5211e4d8a10ea72","tid":1955901,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T20:38:33.000Z","msg":"奶jer人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T21:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"453552d55056be47af545c8b666aaf7719cb25c6","tid":1955901,"uid":128603,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"39249040c2a78d6ef47e26ef039c6eab7ff4dc6e","tid":1955901,"uid":14816,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T20:55:17.000Z","msg":"髮線好高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T21:52:42.